title: Ahh, the comfortable life... Backup in Austin. 1 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Quaint area just North of UT law school, a nicely maintained 10 unit bldg, this ground floor unit is moments away from Hancock Park Golf Course & Hike/Bike trails.', 'High efficiency community washer/dryer takes credit cards or payment by phone app!', 'Flexible lease terms - 1 year at $995/mo or 6-10 month lease @ $1095/mo $75 application fee can submitted online, then deposit can be paid online after approval.', 'Small pets considered.', '*', '**', 'Spectrum (Time Warner) high speed internet & TV included!', ' ***', 'Send Text Message FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 4004220)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas, All Prices)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'PRICES ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE DAILY/PICS MAY NOT REFLECT EXACT UNIT']
